sources.description:
Air Guitar Nation chronicles the birth of the US Air Guitar Championships as legions of aspiring rock stars compete to become the "greatest air guitarist in the world." Two would-be rock legends emerge and strum their way towards glory and the coveted national title.

Directed by Alexandra Lipsitz
2006
Starring         Dan Crane, David Jung
